<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[John`s Dev log]]></title><description><![CDATA[웹 기술에 대한 블로그 입니다.]]></description><link>https://john015.github.io</link><image><url>https://john015.github.io/logos/logo-512.png</url><title>John`s Dev log</title><link>https://john015.github.io</link></image><generator>John`s dev log</generator><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Feb 2019 07:38:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://john015.github.io/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><copyright><![CDATA[All content copyright john015 © 2019 • All rights reserved.]]></copyright><item><title><![CDATA[Introducing react Hooks]]></title><description><![CDATA[어제(2019-02-06) react 16.8.0이 release되면서 드디어 react Hooks가 stable release…]]></description><link>https://john015.github.io/introducing-react-hooks</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://john015.github.io/introducing-react-hooks</guid><category><![CDATA[react]]></category><category><![CDATA[hooks]]></category><category><![CDATA[react 16.8]]></category><pubDate>Thu, 07 Feb 2019 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;어제(2019-02-06) react 16.8.0이 release되면서 드디어 react Hooks가 stable release되었습니다.
제가 사용해보니 몇몇 규칙만 준수하면 상당히 사용 하기 쉽고 이전에 클래스 컴포넌트에서만 할수있었던 기능들을 이제 함수형 컴포넌트에서도 사용 할 수 있게 되었습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;167alpha버전과의-차이점&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#167alpha%EB%B2%84%EC%A0%84%EA%B3%BC%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90&quot; aria-hidden class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;16.7alpha버전과의 차이점&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;먼저 이미 alpha버전을 통해 react hooks에 대해 알고계신분들을 위해 기존에 alpha release된 react hooks와 이번에 stable release 된 react-hooks의 차이점은&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;useMutationEffect&lt;/code&gt; Hooks 삭제&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;useImperativeMethods&lt;/code&gt; Hooks &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;useImperativeHandle&lt;/code&gt;으로 이름 변경&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;useState와 useReducer Hooks 동일한 값 렌더링 불가.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;useEffect / useMemo / useCallback hooks에 전달 된 첫 번째 인자 비교 불가&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;etc..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이 있습니다 더 자세히 알고 싶으시면 &lt;a href=&quot;https://reactjs.org/blog/2019/02/06/react-v16.8.0.html#hooks-changelog-since-alpha-versions&quot;&gt;링크&lt;/a&gt; 를 참고해 주세요&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rules-of-hooks&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#rules-of-hooks&quot; aria-hidden class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Rules of Hooks&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hooks를 사용할려면 몇가지의 규칙을 준수해야합니다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;1-hooks를-컴포넌트의-top-level에서만-사용-해야-합니다&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-hooks%EB%A5%BC-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EC%9D%98-top-level%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EB%A7%8C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%A9%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4&quot; aria-hidden class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1. Hooks를 컴포넌트의 Top-level에서만 사용 해야 합니다.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;반복문, 조건문, 컴포넌트의 내부 함수에서 사용하면 안되고 오직 최상위 함수에서만 사용 해야 합니다.
말보단 코드가 더 이해하기 쉬우니 코드로 설명드리면&lt;/p&gt;
